          "text": "CREATE  FUNCTION [CrisNationalGridWest].[AddDollars] ( @RevisedBilledAmount money,@NetChangeDollars money)\nRETURNS money AS  \r\nBEGIN \r\n    --*******************************************************************************************************************************\r\n    --* Description:  Adds Prior period dollars plus their net change reported equals the \r\n    --*\r\n    --* Peter Heller\r\n    --*   08/31/2010 PAH    created:    \r\n    --*******************************************************************************************************************************\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nreturn isnull(@RevisedBilledAmount,0)+isnull(@NetChangeDollars,0)\r\nEND"
